{"tid":770993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN: 點解香港咁多人訓M記？","createTime":"2018-08-07T14:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T14:28:16.000Z","uid":165773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a27c79872c42f4b9909ae351923a9bc40c12efcc","tid":770993,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"2018年8月7日CNN報導：<br />\n太平山青年商會JCI<br />\n於今年六至七月<br />\n調查了110間M記<br />\n有334人訓M記<br />\n五年前得57人<br />\n<br />\n大部分M記居民都有番工有屋企<br />\n七成表示明明有屋企番<br />\n但係都訓M記因爲<br />\n想慳冷氣 電費或者係<br />\n覺得M記舒服過屋企<br />\n空氣流通 靜D 有Wi-Fi<br />\n食物平<br />\n<br />\n有D真係無屋企<br />\n因為租貴<br />\n2017年Demographia研究指出<br />\n香港97平均尺價770usd<br />\n升到而家1700usd<br />\n係世上其中一個最難令人<br />\n負擔得起既房地產市場<br />\n<br />\n有D因爲屋企人關係差<br />\n同父母不和 或者比老公虐待<br />\n有人因爲老公死左<br />\n覺得訓M記無咁sad<br />\n<br />\nJCI洪小姐表示政府應比多D資源社福機構同update外宿者統計資料 香港人應多關懷身邊既人 包括陌生人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nM記表示會盡量提供舒適環境 唔會趕人走<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2018/08/06/asia/hong-kong-mcdonalds-sleepers-intl/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-mcdonalds-sleepers-intl%2Findex.html&d=60D7r1Bpq9sz4tlH9ThaN2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e9bdc60f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-mcdonalds-sleepers-intl%2Findex.html&h=b8bedeb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2018/08/06/asia/hong-kong-mcdonalds-sleepers-intl/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"09806491d844e8aa7e002e25ca8c06d7a41f834a","tid":770993,"uid":194474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a27c79872c42f4b9909ae351923a9bc40c12efcc","tid":770993,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"2018年8月7日CNN報導：<br />\n太平山青年商會JCI<br />\n於今年六至七月<br />\n調查了110間M記<br />\n有334人訓M記<br />\n五年前得57人<br />\n<br />\n大部分M記居民都有番工有屋企<br />\n七成表示明明有屋企番<br />\n但係都訓M記因爲<br />\n想慳冷氣 電費或者係<br />\n覺得M記舒服過屋企<br />\n空氣流通 靜D 有Wi-Fi<br />\n食物平<br />\n<br />\n有D真係無屋企<br />\n因為租貴<br />\n2017年Demographia研究指出<br />\n香港97平均尺價770usd<br />\n升到而家1700usd<br />\n係世上其中一個最難令人<br />\n負擔得起既房地產市場<br />\n<br />\n有D因爲屋企人關係差<br />\n同父母不和 或者比老公虐待<br />\n有人因爲老公死左<br />\n覺得訓M記無咁sad<br />\n<br />\nJCI洪小姐表示政府應比多D資源社福機構同update外宿者統計資料 香港人應多關懷身邊既人 包括陌生人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nM記表示會盡量提供舒適環境 唔會趕人走<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2018/08/06/asia/hong-kong-mcdonalds-sleepers-intl/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-mcdonalds-sleepers-intl%2Findex.html&d=60D7r1Bpq9sz4tlH9ThaN2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e9bdc60f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-mcdonalds-sleepers-intl%2Findex.html&h=b8bedeb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2018/08/06/asia/hong-kong-mcdonalds-sleepers-intl/index.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T14:18:50.000Z","msg":"如果有得返屋企佢地神早返左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a374156dfdd912da82150c93e42a700e677f39","tid":770993,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T14:23:02.000Z","msg":"屋企無冷氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f982b4259188e992ca8a3898063e21918d12e691","tid":770993,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"瞓維園好過"}]}